# Bühlmann ZHL-12 M-value lines for all 16 tissue compartments
# Source: Bühlmann, A.A. (1984). Decompression--Decompression Sickness.
#         Springer-Verlag, Berlin. Table 8, p. 26.
#
# M-value equation (Bühlmann form): P_amb_tol = (P_t - a) * b
# Inverted for plotting:             P_t_max   =  a + P_amb / b
#
# ZHL-12 nitrogen coefficients (a in bar, b dimensionless):
# Comp | N2 T_half (min) |   a     |   b
#   1  |    2.65         | 2.200   | 0.820   <- same a,b for He and N2, comps 1-9
#   2  |    7.94         | 1.500   | 0.820
#   3  |   12.2          | 1.080   | 0.825
#   4  |   18.5          | 0.900   | 0.835
#   5  |   26.5          | 0.750   | 0.845
#   6  |   37.0          | 0.580   | 0.860
#   7  |   53.0          | 0.470   | 0.870
#   8  |   79.0          | 0.455   | 0.890
#   9  |  114.0          | 0.455   | 0.890
#  10  |  146.0          | 0.455   | 0.934   <- N2-specific values, comps 10-16
#  11  |  185.0          | 0.380   | 0.934
#  12  |  238.0          | 0.255   | 0.962
#  13  |  304.0          | 0.255   | 0.962
#  14  |  397.0          | 0.255   | 0.962
#  15  |  503.0          | 0.255   | 0.962
#  16  |  635.0          | 0.255   | 0.962
#
# Three index blocks separated by two blank lines:
#   Block 0: All 16 M-value lines  (P_amb vs P_t_max)
#   Block 1: P_t = P_amb reference (no supersaturation)
